To make a MacOS package, start packagemaker from /Developer/Applications/Utilities/PackageMaker.
Set Organization: com.Agilent
    Minimum target Leopard.
Select menu Project/AddContents...
Use browser to select Package_contents
  then select VnmrJ.app  (the VJ picture should show in Contents.)
Unclick Allow Relocation choice.
Click Scripts Choice. Use Browser for 
   Scripts directory:
to select install_resources
Click Configuration, use browser to select
   Destination: /Applications
   Unselect "Allow custom location"
   Package Identifier: com.Agilent.VnmrJ31A.pkg
Click Area below "Contents" on the left and then set
   Choice Name: VnmrJ31A
Click "Untitled Package: area, then Configuration. Set
   Title: VnmrJ31A
Select "System volume" deselect others.
Click "Edit Installer"
Drop Splash screen and select To-Fit. (git-repo/software/vnmrbg_iconlib/Splash_VnmrJ.png)
Drop Readme file at appropriate time. (git-repo/software/macos/ReadMe.txt)
Drop License file at appropriate time. (git-repo/3rdParty/SFU/installer/AgilentSoftwareLicenseAgreement.rtf)
Click Build. Set Save As: VnmrJ31A in cdimageNVJ directory
